adhocMessage1.value: To facilitate system update, the Internet filing service will be temporarily suspended from 20 March 2015. Any partially completed return previously saved will also be deleted. Please complete your filing ON OR BEFORE 19 March 2015 or you will have to file your tax return in paper form. (testing)

adhocMessage1Chn.value: 為方便進行系統更新工作，「網上報稅」將於2015年3月20日起暫停服務，所有暫存未提交的報稅表資料亦將會被刪除。請於2015年3月19日或之前完成你的網上報稅。否則，你須以文本方式提交報稅表。 （測試）

adhocMessageSelectPartsChn.value: 為方便你填報，本局已根據報稅表發出當日本局的記錄及你上年度的報稅表，替你預填部分資料。請核對有關資料，並作出適當修改。請注意，你有責任確保所有填報的資料正確無誤，並無遺漏。

attentionNote.value: For your convenience, certain input fields are pre-filled with data extracted from IRD records as at the TAX RETURN ISSUE DATE and your tax return for last year. Please check the data and amend them as appropriate. It is your responsibility to ensure all data input are correct and that there is no omission.

For your convenience, certain input fields are pre-filled with data extracted from your tax return for last year. Please check the data and amend them as appropriate. If the pre-filled data is not applicable to current year, click the relevant button to clear them. It is your responsibility to ensure that all data input are correct and there is no omission.

For your convenience, the employment particulars are pre-filled with data extracted from IRD records as at 10/05/2022. The availability of your current year income amount details is dependent on when the Employer's Returns are filed. Please check the data and amend them as appropriate. It is your responsibility to ensure all data input are correct and that there is no omission. If you have amended any of the pre-filled income amounts, please consider leave your reason in the text box of "Supplementary Information on Tax Return" by clicking the "Supplement" button at the bottom of the screen.
